The address of the '''Hagakure Society''' is c/o [[Saga Prefectural Library]], Jonai 1, [[Saga, Saga|Saga]], [[Japan]], 840. It is a scholarly association devoted to study and interpretation of the [[Samurai of Saga Han]]. It publishes a quarterly journal, in Japanese, and authorizes books, articles, and public meetings and lectures related to the ethics and cultural history of [[Saga Prefecture|Saga]] and its citizens.

